data.description: If you are searching for the ideal farmhouse this is it. Welcome home! This 5 plus bedroom/3 bath home with an office and Rec room/media room and workout room (currently used as a bedroom) is move in ready. This home features hardwood floors throughout, open concept kitchen, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops with custom subway tile backsplash, huge rock fireplace with gas logs, custom built ins, oversized 2 car garage, master on main level with a newly remodeled master bath (March 2019), large covered back deck overlooking the oversized in-ground pool with custom fencing and lit stacked rock columns. The pool has been professionally maintained weekly by Mattheson Pools. The landscaping and drip watering system were designed and installed by Zone Seven. All new electrical switches and tamper proof electrical outlets installed August 2019 throughout the home home. Also on the property is a turn of the century two story barn and a cinder block storage building if you need extra storage. This home comes with 2.52 acres but is surrounded by 100+ undeveloped acreage so you truly feel like you're living the farm life but without all the upkeep. Close proximity to Walhalla schools (golf cart ride to the new Walhalla High School) Priced below recent appraisal. Owner is a licensed SC Realtor
